Package: voro
Title: R interface to the Voro++ software library
Description: Voro++ (http://math.lbl.gov/voro++) is an open source software library for the computation of the Voronoi diagram, a widely-used tessellation that has applications in many scientific fields. This package wraps the library and provides an R interface.
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2021-02-10
